You can write a class which implements that interface:

```java
class MatchFirstChar implements Function&lt;String,Boolean&gt; {
  private final char c;
  MatchFirstChar(char c) {
    this.c = c;
  }
  Boolean apply(String s) {
    return s.charAt(0) == c;
  } 
}
```
and then use it:
```java
